        <h1 class="detail__title detail__title--home">Hello, my name <br>is Joel Goodman.</h1>
        <div class="detail__body">
          <p>I've spent nearly two decades helping college and universities make better digital decisions through strategy, design, front-end development, and a deep belief that the web should treat people well. That conviction became the <a href="https://bravery.co/insight/hospitable-design-framework/?utm_source=jgg">Hospitable Design</a> framework, which has guided my work across dozens of university website projects.</p>
          <p>Today I lead growth strategy at <a href="https://squiz.net/?utm_source=joelgoodman">Squiz</a>, where I focus on demand generation, digital strategy, and generative engine optimization. I'm particularly vocal about how AI search is reshaping content discoverability, and how most institutions aren't ready for it. I also take on limited consulting engagements focused on higher education web intelligence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
